cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.MM 

This paper deals with learning deep visual object models from noisy web data, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques for creating web datasets. Finally, the paper applies the learned models to a mobile robot vision task (cs.MM).
